<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>I.S.Tech-{{product.name}}</title>

    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet"
        integrity="sha384-QWTKZyjpPEjISv5WaRU9OFeRpok6YctnYmDr5pNlyT2bRjXh0JMhjY6hW+ALEwIH" crossorigin="anonymous">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/style-details.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/app.js">

    <style>
        .listCard {
            max-height: 600px;
            /* Set the maximum height for the cart list */
            overflow-y: auto;
            /* Add vertical scroll when content overflows */
            padding: 10px;
            /* Add padding */
        }

        .checkoutBtn {
            background-color: #4caf50;
            /* Change background color */
            color: white;
            border: none;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            /* Adjust padding */
            border-radius: 5px;
            /* Add border-radius for button */
            cursor: pointer;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>

    <!-- Navbar -->
    <nav class="navbar  navbar-light navbar-expand-lg fixed-top" style="background-color:#202D42;">
        <a class="navbar-brand" href="/index_after_signedin"><img src="/images/Logo.png" alt="I.S.Tech"
                style="width:70px ;height:70px"></a>
        <button class="navbar-toggler" type="button" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#navbarSupportedContent"
            aria-controls="navbarSupportedContent" aria-expanded="false" aria-label="Toggle navigation">
            <span class="navbar-toggler-icon"></span>
        </button>

        <div class="collapse navbar-collapse" id="navbarSupportedContent">
            <div class="one">
                <ul class="navbar-nav mr-auto" class="one">
                    <li class="nav-item active">
                        <a class="nav-link tc" href="/index_after_signedin">Home</a>
                    </li>
                    <li class="nav-item">
                        <a class="nav-link tc" href="#Our_block">About</a>
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            <input type="text" id="twotabsearchtextbox" placeholder="Search"
                class="nav-input nav-progressive-attribute">
            <div class="mx-1">
                <button class="btn btn-outline-warning">Search</button>
                <a href="/logout"><button class="btn btn-outline-danger">Logout</button></a>
            </div>
        </div>

        <header>
            <div class="shopping">
                <img src="/images/shopping.png">
                <span class="quantity">0</span>
            </div>
        </header>

        <div class="list"></div>

        <div class="card">
            <strong><b>
                    <h1>Cart</h1>
                </b></strong>
            <ul class="listCard">
            </ul>
            <div class="checkOut">
                <div class="total">0</div>
                <button class="checkoutBtn" onclick="window.location.href='/buynow'">Buy Now</button>
                <div class="closeShopping">Close</div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </nav>

    <div class="space"></div>
    <div class="mycontainer">
        <div id="carouselExample" class="carousel slide carousel-fade">
            <div id="carouselloginIndicators" class="carousel slide carousel-fade" data-ride="carousel ">
                <div class="carousel-inner">
                    <div class="carousel-item active">
                        <img class="d-block w-0" src="/images/{{ product.img1 }}" alt="First slide">
                    </div>
                    <div class="carousel-item">
                        <img class="d-block w-0" src="/images/{{ product.img2 }}" alt="Second slide">
                    </div>
                    <div class="carousel-item">
                        <img class="d-block w-0" src="/images/{{ product.img3 }}" alt="Third slide">
                    </div>
                </div>
                <a class="carousel-control-prev" href="#carouselloginIndicators" role="button" data-slide="prev">
                    <span class="carousel-control-prev-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
                </a>
                <a class="carousel-control-next" href="#carouselloginIndicators" role="button" data-slide="next">
                    <span class="carousel-control-next-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
                </a>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="name">
            {{!-- Product Name --}}
            {{ product.name }}

            <div class="price">
                Rs. {{ product.price }}
            </div>

            <div class="btn1">
                <button class="btn1" onclick="window.location.href='/buynow'">Buy Now</button>
            </div>
            <button class="btn1" onclick="addToCart('{{ product.name }}', '{{ product.price }}','{{product.img2}}')">Add
                to Cart</button>


            <div>
                <p class="properties">
                    <b>Details in depth:</b>
                    {{ product.in_detail }} {{ product.ram }} {{ product.storage }}
                </p>
                <p class="properties">
                    <b>Display:</b>
                    {{ product.Display }}
                </p>
                <p class="properties">
                    <b>RAM:</b>
                    {{ product.ram }}
                </p>
                <p class="properties">
                    <b>Storage:</b>
                    {{ product.storage }}
                </p>

                <p class="properties">
                    <b>{{ product.name }}</b>
                    {{ product.detail }} {{ product.Display }}
                </p>
                <p class="properties">
                    <b>Performance: </b>
                    {{ product.performance }}
                </p>

                <p class="properties">
                    <b>Other Features: </b>
                    {{ product.otherFeatures }}
            </div>


        </div>

    </div>

    <div class="review">
        <div class="texxt">
            CUSTOMER REVIEWS
        </div>

        <div class="customer">
            <div class="customer-name">
                Sahil Gupta
            </div>

            <div>
                <p>It's amazing machine by apple. I am very impressed with it's performance.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="customer-name">
                Suban Shaikh
            </div>

            <div>
                <p>Great for my college work. Works perfectly</p>
            </div>
            <div class="customer-name">
                Sneha H.
            </div>

            <div>
                <p>Today I got the product and it was well packed and there was no problem with product . I will surely
                    recommend this product to every student or professional to buy this MacBook Pro M2.......</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <script src="/app.js"></script>
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"
        integrity="sha384-JKJqfJTgZvrnPTvZFwnl5JaZlGB7f+rS8zH/jyLS+Dm9f+kgDp4h9g6B48vGqOq4"
        crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
    <script src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.3.1.slim.min.js"
        integrity="sha384-q8i/X+965DzO0rT7abK41JStQIAqVgRVzpbzo5smXKp4YfRvH+8abtTE1Pi6jizo"
        crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/popper.js@1.14.3/dist/umd/popper.min.js"
        integrity="sha384-ZMP7rVo3mIykV+2+9J3UJ46jBk0WLaUAdn689aCwoqbBJiSnjAK/l8WvCWPIPm49"
        crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@4.1.3/dist/js/bootstrap.min.js"
        integrity="sha384-ChfqqxuZUCnJSK3+MXmPNIyE6ZbWh2IMqE241rYiqJxyMiZ6OW/JmZQ5stwEULTy"
        crossorigin="anonymous"></script>

</body>

</html>